{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-f606af09-08d1-40d8-a374-54d7930ba3cd-16\nfc_47175aea-66f9-9faf-a737-b854a4065ab9_5","tool_call":{"grepToolCall":{"args":{"pattern":"mailbox_open|CallIntent|voicemail_listened|listenedAt","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","context":5,"caseInsensitive":false,"multiline":false,"toolCallId":"call-f606af09-08d1-40d8-a374-54d7930ba3cd-16\nfc_47175aea-66f9-9faf-a737-b854a4065ab9_5","offset":0},"result":{"success":{"pattern":"mailbox_open|CallIntent|voicemail_listened|listenedAt","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","outputMode":"content","workspaceResults":{"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine":{"content":{"matches":[{"file":"docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":6,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":7,"content":"## 1. 主链","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":8,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":9,"content":"```text","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":10,"content":"选定 User → 加载 PlayerProfile","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":11,"content":"CallIntent","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":12,"content":"  → CallCardResolver","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":13,"content":"  → 绑定 CallCardInstance；beginCall → CallSession（frozenCard + ComposeScene）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":14,"content":"  → ContextComposer（只读；promptScenes + 本地时间）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":15,"content":"  → DialogueAdapter.start(DialogueSessionSpec)","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":16,"content":"  → … DialogueEvent …（工具只登记 RuntimeExitCandidate）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":28,"content":"- **active ≠ completed**；`call.ended ≠ story.card.completed`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":29,"content":"- Story 挂机后 Effect 可跨角色 `patch_memory`；Free 走总管线而非强制 exits。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":30,"content":"- **`cardKind=voicemail` 永不进 `Board.pending`**；进信箱靠 attach/schedule 分流 + 物化（见 §8.4–§8.5）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":31,"content":"- 对话通道见 [50](./50-对话与模型适配.md)。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":32,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":33,"content":"## 2. CallIntent（逻辑输入）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":34,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":35,"content":"引擎不依赖话机 GPIO；只认逻辑意图：","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":36,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":37,"content":"```ts","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":38,"content":"type CallIntent =","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":39,"content":"  | { kind: \"user_dial\"; agentId: string }","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":40,"content":"  | { kind: \"agent_outbound\"; agentId: string; instanceId?: string }","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":41,"content":"  | { kind: \"redial\"; agentId: string }           // 来自重播槽","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":42,"content":"  | { kind: \"simulate_start\"; cardId: string }    // 调试器：从某卡强制开始","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":43,"content":"  | { kind: \"mailbox_open\"; agentId: string; voicemailId: string; cardId: string }","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":44,"content":"  // 信箱打开：听已物化留言；Resolver / beginCall 绑定该 voicemail 卡（entryMode=mailbox_open）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":45,"content":"```","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":46,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":47,"content":"**听留言路径（钉死）：** 用户/调试打开信箱条目 → `mailbox_open` → `beginCall`（`frozenCard` = 该 `cardKind=voicemail` 卡，`interactionMode=playback_only`）→ 播槽内 text/audioRef → Outcome（`voicemail_listened` / `playback_completed` / `playback_skipped` 等）→ ExitSelector → 该卡 `exits`。**不推荐**壳自播完只打 flag、Host 另写无 Session 的 exits 捷径。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":48,"content":"## 3. CallCardResolver","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":49,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":50,"content":"### 3.1 输入","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":51,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":52,"content":"- `intent: CallIntent`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":53,"content":"- `board: CallCardBoard`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":54,"content":"- `package: StoryPackage`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":55,"content":"- `redialSlot?: { agentId: string; cardId?: string }`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":56,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":57,"content":"### 3.2 规则（v1）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":58,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":59,"content":"在 **当前 Profile** 上：","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":60,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":61,"content":"1. `simulate_start`：直接激活指定 `cardId` 的新 Instance（或已有 pending），忽略日常优先级。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":62,"content":"2. `redial`：若槽指向 `cardId`，优先激活该 Definition 在目标角色上的对应 pending；若无 pending，可按包配置挂卡再激活（校验器应警告「重播未挂卡」）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":63,"content":"3. `mailbox_open`：按信箱槽 `voicemailId` + `cardId` 绑定该 **`cardKind=voicemail`** Definition；**不**从 `Board.pending` 挑选；Session 强制 `playback_only` + `entryMode=mailbox_open`。播槽内已物化内容。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":64,"content":"4. `user_dial` / `agent_outbound`：","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":65,"content":"   - **有效可拨**：`effectiveDialable = !def.isNarrativeOnly && ((def.dialable === true) || (runtime?.unlocked === true))`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":66,"content":"   - 若意图为 `user_dial` 且 `!effectiveDialable` → `CHARACTER_NOT_DIALABLE`；`agent_outbound` / `simulate_start` 仍允许（**narrative-only 除外**：外呼亦拒绝，除非调试 force）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":67,"content":"   - **禁止**把 `cardKind=voicemail` 解析为待接通剧情卡（voicemail 永不在 pending）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":68,"content":"   - 在目标 `pending` 中筛选 `entryMode` 匹配的 Instance（拨号：`inbound_user_dial|either`（及 `inbound` 别名）；外呼：`outbound_auto|either`（及 `outbound` / `agent_outbound` 别名））。**`redialSlot` 仅作优先，不过 mode 则跳过**（见 `pickPendingForIntent`）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true}]}],"totalLines":53,"totalMatchedLines":8,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-f606af09-08d1-40d8-a374-54d7930ba3cd-16\nfc_47175aea-66f9-9faf-a737-b854a4065ab9_5","startedAtMs":"1784792683726","completedAtMs":"1784792684046"},"model_call_id":"38ac4e31-68ba-4988-a00f-708e88213e1d-4-uwpl","session_id":"001d8657-5fdc-4284-95ab-d8d3e6836461","timestamp_ms":1784792684041}
